.max-w-4xl.mx-auto
  %h1.font-bold.text-4xl.text-center.mb-8 About Multipost
  .bg-white.rounded-lg.shadow-md.p-8.mb-8
    %h2.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-4 Our Mission
    %p.text-gray-700.mb-6
      At Multipost, we're on a mission to simplify social media management for creators, businesses, and marketers.
      We believe that creating and sharing content should be efficient, allowing you to focus on what matters most -
      engaging with your audience and growing your online presence.
    %h2.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-4 What We Offer
    .grid.md:grid-cols-2.gap-6.mb-6
      .border.border-gray-200.rounded.p-4
        %h3.font-semibold.text-xl.mb-2 Multi-Platform Publishing
        %p.text-gray-600 Create content once and publish it across all your social networks with customization for each platform.
      .border.border-gray-200.rounded.p-4
        %h3.font-semibold.text-xl.mb-2 Content Calendar
        %p.text-gray-600 Plan and schedule your posts with our intuitive drag-and-drop calendar interface.
      .border.border-gray-200.rounded.p-4
        %h3.font-semibold.text-xl.mb-2 Analytics Dashboard
        %p.text-gray-600 Track performance across platforms with unified analytics and custom reporting.
      .border.border-gray-200.rounded.p-4
        %h3.font-semibold.text-xl.mb-2 Team Collaboration
        %p.text-gray-600 Work together with role-based permissions, approval workflows, and shared assets.
  .bg-white.rounded-lg.shadow-md.p-8.mb-8
    %h2.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-4 Our Story
    %p.text-gray-700.mb-4
      Multipost was founded in 2023 by a team of social media professionals who were frustrated with
      the complexity and time-consuming nature of managing multiple social accounts. We built the tool
      we wished existed - one that combines power with simplicity.
    %p.text-gray-700
      Today, we're proud to help thousands of users save time and improve their social media presence
      through our constantly evolving platform.
  .text-center
    %h2.text-2xl.font-semibold.mb-6 Ready to streamline your social media workflow?
    - if user_signed_in?
      %p.mb-4 You're already part of the Multipost family. Thank you for your trust!
      %a.bg-blue-600.hover:bg-blue-700.text-white.px-6.py-2.rounded-lg.inline-block.transition-colors{ href: "#" } Go to Dashboard
    - else
      .flex.justify-center.space-x-4
        = link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        = link_to "Contact Us", pages_contact_path, class: "bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
